name: Courseutil
body:
### Welcome to CourseUtil page.

CourseUtil is an ImageJ Plugin used for teaching in the EMBL Image Processing and Analysis course. 

### Downloads
For downloading the plugin jar file, please click [here](https://github.com/cmci/CourseUtil/blob/gh-pages/target/EMBL_sampleimages-1.0.0.jar?raw=true). 

FOr downloading the source, please click .zip or tarball icon at the top-right. 

### Support or Contact
Check out the documentation at http://cmci.embl.de/downloads/sampleimageloader or contact miura@embl.de
